{"tid":230711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北京電影人：駐港部隊捐血量佔全港獻血量六成","createTime":"2017-05-05T14:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T01:53:49.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":73,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"42ba8afa1fbcc0dd4925b41d3505b86650d34c95","tid":230711,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:17:36.000Z","msg":"北京電影人網上亂吹遭攻陷<br />\n<br />\n轉載：新報<br />\n<br />\n「駐港部隊捐血量佔全港獻血量六成」<br />\n北京電影人網上亂吹遭攻陷<br />\n<br />\n【新報訊】繼年初北京大學教授孔慶東罵港人是狗，遭港人口誅筆伐後，另一名北京電影人趙宇寧前日在微博，寫下了「駐港部隊捐血量佔香港全部獻血量的六成」的留言，再次觸動香港巿民的神經，在微博留言反擊。<br />\n<br />\n「孔慶東罵港人是狗」、「廣東道名店禁止港人拍照」及「雙非孕婦來港產子」等事件，令港人受辱及認為社會資源被掠奪，因而產生抗拒內地人的情緒。但港人被矮化事件仍然層出不窮，兩日前，北京電影人趙宇寧微博留言：「駐港官兵數千人每年義務獻血量，居然是香港全部獻血量的60%？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暗踩要靠內地人獻血<br />\n<br />\n這句話觸動港人網民的神經，因為這句話雖無前文後理，卻被網民認為抬高駐港官兵在港獻血的偉大，又暗踩港人要靠內地人獻血，趙宇寧的微博迅即被港人攻陷。<br />\n<br />\n港人網民做足功課才反擊，先後找出港人捐血量及駐港部隊捐血量比對，香港紅十字會輸血服務中心，在6月3日公布11年有近17萬市民捐出逾23萬袋血液，製成近60萬單位的血製品給病人治療，創下輸血服務中心60年的新紀錄。而人民網在同年9月12日報道，駐港部隊14年來累計逾5000名官兵獻血逾230萬毫升。<br />\n<br />\n網民表示，紅十字會每日要用700包血，每包血450毫升計，一日要30萬毫升，14年捐血總重量，僅夠約8天應用。而且香港捐血屬義務，趙不應為了擦鞋誇大駐港部隊的偉大。<br />\n<br />\n另一名網民認為，港人700餘萬，駐港部隊約8000人，「0.115%的人獻了60%的血，大陸人到香港生孩子，香港還呼天搶地要修法，這樣寵養，人心就回歸了嗎?」"},{"pid":"fd6266905ddd6370f0ce8bbd44823c691f8b449a","tid":230711,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:19:54.000Z","msg":"反正點吹班傻閪大圈仔都會信"},{"pid":"85911548ecebcca9fa3bae82039e70f3a748e4c1","tid":230711,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:20:14.000Z","msg":"諗起mad max d 人型血袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a94af042d7c93cfcab9e30f37701aa57303644","tid":230711,"uid":41116,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:25:26.000Z","msg":"上年33萬人次捐血，支那駐港部隊得6000人<br />\n6成即係198000<br />\n198000/6000=每人33次<br />\n每11日就捐一次<br />\n真係能人所不能"},{"pid":"fc02ea13eb80dddb3e818e35c178d35b53a99fbf","tid":230711,"uid":56636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:25:40.000Z","msg":"又要唔要澄清啊"},{"pid":"53698fd2e476842d1e3450dd4191427ab781ad08","tid":230711,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:26:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bbf2da39436dfd86e4eadc07ea7673862c1ba99","tid":230711,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:28:06.000Z","msg":"事撚但啦<br />\n支那人捐血俾返支那人用，關我撚事咩<br />\n但香港人捐血俾支那人用，就老閪都唔撚得"},{"pid":"357c1dc6a2f9bbecc05736b0891c209f8a6c20f9","tid":230711,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:28:27.000Z","msg":"大陸人都有份用架wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f8b78ecdd8c210dfc9dc3c56035539ab76b129e","tid":230711,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:28:43.000Z","msg":"俾我估中 大陸五毛係想俾個錯誤印象其他人<br />\n <br />\n想講到香港人唔捐血捐到唔夠血 而唔係因爲大陸人做手術 雙非用多左香港人血"},{"pid":"a3e8c5a6be870cdd620f43d3c5dc159c05c81014","tid":230711,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:30:59.000Z","msg":"哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"538b164c5d980f3198effa3b3b1937a056feda61","tid":230711,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:32:07.000Z","msg":"6成咁少？唔講夠9成？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a59d0e1adc8c05a388b649e19a241cc9ae0ad0","tid":230711,"uid":71676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:32:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上年33萬人次捐血，支那駐港部隊得6000人<br />\n6成即係198000<br />\n198000/6000=每人33次<br />\n每11日就捐一次<br />\n真係能人所不能</blockquote><br />\n信共產黨得永生 我細細個就知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5d02e26689a5af217786ef7640e747773cd4cc","tid":230711,"uid":18962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:38:23.000Z","msg":"正 貼俾紅十字會睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac6c8047cf54098c20d2a4dcb4e2c66678a86d7","tid":230711,"uid":26671,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:38:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日(17.08.2016)解放軍駐港部隊，舉行自一九九八年來第十九次捐血活動，共有四百名官兵參加，當中女軍人佔十五人，<span style=\"color: red;\">預計歷來合共有七千六百名官兵參與捐血</span>，捐血約三百三十八萬毫升。有第一次參與捐血的女兵表示，以往曾經嘗試捐血，但因血壓低而未能成功，今次特意在捐血前喝糖水，有點怕痛但不緊張，認為捐血是非常好的公益活動。有第二次捐血的士兵指出，對為香港市民捐血感到自豪和激動。駐港部隊副司令員廖正榮指出，駐港部隊一直堅決貫徹一國兩制、《基本法》及《駐軍法》，堅決維護社會公眾利益，深化和香港各界溝通。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n十九年先得七千六次個人捐血<br />\n計翻即係一年得四百人捐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n計翻上面講2011年香港人捐血係23萬次<br />\n即係只有0.17%嘅血係駐軍捐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  算係稍為比佢地佔嘅總人口比 (0.115%) 高少少咁"},{"pid":"6909005f56eac106b43d25c6acae5a3047ae1b4d","tid":230711,"uid":61653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:40:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支那<br />\n什麼都做假"},{"pid":"02931df7a41051772e2a029d42dcb2481b53ea04","tid":230711,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:42:16.000Z","msg":"我地用左支那血都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c02a233af264c5865e238f4176a9cd42f0674ba8","tid":230711,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:44:07.000Z","msg":"如果用5000人榨曬啲血岀嚟夠香港幾多日用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea8a2aa24030162aae09383740621f5a79d6468","tid":230711,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:44:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上年33萬人次捐血，支那駐港部隊得6000人<br />\n6成即係198000<br />\n198000/6000=每人33次<br />\n每11日就捐一次<br />\n真係能人所不能</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f75f324c55711efcdf8395fae2db567a7efe8763","tid":230711,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:46:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73e4e421919b71174c67ccc6d338c85afe2c9160","tid":230711,"uid":10682,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:48:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上年33萬人次捐血，支那駐港部隊得6000人<br />\n6成即係198000<br />\n198000/6000=每人33次<br />\n每11日就捐一次<br />\n真係能人所不能</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那狗真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16b202b55b980a983f3c2fad855619b601db876","tid":230711,"uid":26671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:50:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果用5000人榨曬啲血岀嚟夠香港幾多日用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成年人around 5000ml，5000人 x 5000 ml = 二千五百萬ml<br />\n<br />\n香港一年用血好似係around 8千幾萬ml<br />\n<br />\n即係大約可以用到幾個月"},{"pid":"a65fc9c2e19266ecafed33d97e93c8441b8455b6","tid":230711,"uid":1333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:50:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上年33萬人次捐血，支那駐港部隊得6000人<br />\n6成即係198000<br />\n198000/6000=每人33次<br />\n每11日就捐一次<br />\n真係能人所不能</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n計錯<br />\n<br />\n係平均一年四百人捐198000次"},{"pid":"4f2e07c3c46d22866d46e67e19be779f478f8120","tid":230711,"uid":27451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05